hopobject.body: Where do you live? orphan medical device Certain diseases appear during adolescence, around the same time as the HPV and other vaccines are given. Some parents may worry that the two are linked. However, Weinbaum said they have been unable to find any links. "We've been doing a systematic review of medical records in managed care systems for any adverse events that occur after vaccination with the HPV vaccine and we haven't seen anything other than fainting."
